      "title": "The Parliament will be suspended for 24 hours",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe has informed the party leaders that he will suspend Parliament for 24 hours. Parliament Member Mano Ganesan says that the President announced that Parliament will be closed for 24 hours for a new ceremonial start."
